===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: chŏp
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ʧɒp/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /tSQp/

===Noun===

# A cut of meat, often containing a section of a [[rib]].
# A blow with an [[axe]], [[cleaver]], or similar [[utensil]].
# [[Ocean]] [[wave]]s, generally caused by [[wind]], distinguished from [[swell]] by being smaller and not lasting as long.

